# project-druzya monorepo

Services live in `services/<name>/`. Each is **independent**:

- own `Makefile`, `AGENTS.md`, `.golangci.yml`, `go.mod`
- own `scripts/dev/docker-compose.yml`
- own `.cursor/rules/`

When editing code, **cd into `services/<name>/`** and follow that service's `AGENTS.md`. New service: copy [services/template/](../services/template/). **Registry checklist:** [.cursor/rules/service-registry.mdc](service-registry.mdc) + [deploy/scripts/services.conf.sh](../deploy/scripts/services.conf.sh).

Keep `AGENTS.md` in sync with code — see [.cursor/rules/agents-md.mdc](agents-md.mdc).
